title: El Al
description: El Al is an Israeli national airline known for its distinctive color palette. The deep blue-gray (RGB: 19, 17, 55), often associated with reliability and professionalism, along with the warm beige-gray (RGB: 145, 137, 120), known to evoke a sense of calm and comfort, can be seen prominently in its branding and aircraft livery. These colors help to establish a strong and recognizable presence in the aviation industry.
